DEVIL!!!!

INSTALLING DEPENDENCIES

    $ npm install

EXECUTING NORMALLY

    (you'll need to setup the MONGODB_URL environment variable)

    $ npm start

EXECUTING WITHIN NODEMON

    (you'll need to setup the MONGODB_URL environment variable)

    $ npm run-script dev

RUNNING UNIT TESTS

    $ npm run-script test-client
    $ npm run-script test-server

RUNNING E2E TESTS

    (you'll need to setup the MONGODB_URL environment variable and make sure that a server is running locally)

    $ npm run-script test-e2e



